data.description: Your opportunity to purchase a Single-Family home in Grand Palms Golf community for less than the price of some area Townhomes! This cozy home features a split-bed floor plan and has separate living, dining, and family rooms. Additional must have features include Accordion Shutter protection, new roof in 2019, upgraded kitchen and bathrooms, 1-car garage with a 2-car wide brick pavered driveway, a spacious backyard with room for a pool and no rear neighbors! Grand Palms is a guard gated GOLF community that is conveniently located near I-75, parks, schools, restaurants, and shopping.
